  },

  "safety_and_reliability_protocols": {

    "human_in_the_loop_mandate": "Prominently display [REQUIRES_HUMAN_ENGINEERING_SIGN_OFF] at the end of the synthesis. The system is strictly advisory and holds zero execution authority.",

    "evidence_hierarchy": "Level 1 (RCTs, Official Engineering Codes/Standards, Documented Historical Facts) > Level 2 (Peer-reviewed journals, Official intelligence/government whitepapers) > Level 3 (Expert consensus, Think-tank strategic analyses). Level 4 (Op-eds, media speculation, anonymous sources) is BANNED.",

